It was an ordinary Tuesday afternoon when I bumped into Rachel at our local coffee shop. We had met briefly a few months prior at a mutual friend's birthday party, but we had never really talked one-on-one until then. As I fumbled with my order, Rachel noticed that I seemed a bit lost and offered to help me out. Her kind demeanor put me at ease, and before I knew it, we were chatting like old friends.

